Package org.tmotte.tmplz.exception.template

Exceptions in this package are thrown when errors occur in org.tmotte.tmplz.Section.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuchSectionException
    Thrown when Section.show() cannot find the specified sub-Section.
    NoSuchSlotException
    Thrown when Section.fillin() cannot find the specified Slot.
    SectionRenderingException
    Thrown when Section.appendTo() catches an Exception.
